{"tid":1656162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請為陳彥霖伸冤","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T11:03:07.000Z","uid":126209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc8975356f4797924313e3807c72734d8274596","tid":1656162,"uid":126209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1qY4Fv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1qY4Fv.png&h=b695333c&s={SIZE}\" />又出口述<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位同事：<br />\n <br />\n過去數天，大家也為青年學院陳同學的逝世感到難過，我們希望藉此讓大家知悉校方的跟進工作。<br />\n <br />\n陳同學為青年學院本學年新生，於開學前告假兩周，於9月16日回校上課，並於9月20日缺課，院校老師隨即跟進並與家人聯絡，了解情況。其後家人就事件報警求助，校方亦一直與家人保持聯絡。在9月27日我們知悉不幸事件後，已即時通知相關教職員及同學，並安排學生發展處的學生輔導主任提供支援及輔導。學生發展處亦會繼續為有需要的同學提供支援及輔導。<br />\n <br />\n我們十分明白同事對事件的關心，其實院校和大家一樣，十分關注事件。就CCTV 紀錄，我們已公開陳同學傍晚回校及離校片段如下：<br />\n <br />\n片段一：<br />\n<a href=\"https://connectvtc-my.sharepoint.com/:v:/g/personal/extuser01_connect_vtc_edu_hk/EZK92OtluwZBhD5-xTvRP5UBuSg8cv9-e-5N3b2uHmeWhA?e=bIhG6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconnectvtc-my.sharepoint.com%2F%3Av%3A%2Fg%2Fpersonal%2Fextuser01_connect_vtc_edu_hk%2FEZK92OtluwZBhD5-xTvRP5UBuSg8cv9-e-5N3b2uHmeWhA%3Fe%3DbIhG6s&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=35f802f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://connectvtc-my.sharepoint.com/:v:/g/personal/extuser01_connect_vtc_edu_hk/EZK92OtluwZBhD5-xTvRP5UBuSg8cv9-e-5N3b2uHmeWhA?e=bIhG6s</a><br />\n <br />\n片段二：<br />\n請先按以下連結下載軟件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://connectvtc-my.sharepoint.com/:u:/g/personal/extuser01_connect_vtc_edu_hk/EbSPRCzhCzdMoicL4IRPfFsBdPg5YZsG3Kl7o5jOxvenJQ?e=FI4aEu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconnectvtc-my.sharepoint.com%2F%3Au%3A%2Fg%2Fpersonal%2Fextuser01_connect_vtc_edu_hk%2FEbSPRCzhCzdMoicL4IRPfFsBdPg5YZsG3Kl7o5jOxvenJQ%3Fe%3DFI4aEu&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=5468cb55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: